text: Charles Sabouret (born 8 June 1884, date of death unknown) was a French figure skater. He participated in the Olympic Games in Antwerp 1920 (seventh place) and Chamonix 1924 (ninth place) in Pair Skating along with Simone Sabouret. == References == ==External links== * Category:1884 births Category:Year of death missing Category:French male pair skaters Category:Figure skaters at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Figure skaters at the 1924 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic figure skaters of France
